{"tid":2328840,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"侵侵唔打算出軍事法庭就唔該早D放棄","createTime":"2020-12-16T21:29:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-17T15:41:55.000Z","uid":130385,"like":45,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"86425f37df19b321e3d261a268a6aacbd57c5712","tid":2328840,"uid":130385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T21:29:42.000Z","msg":"小弟本身都係侵粉 但係見到侵侵依家全部活路都差唔多封哂  議會同最高法院睇落都係浪費時間<br />\n得返軍事法庭 出動軍隊係唯一勝算   再拖落去  去到1月佢點唔認輸都要落台    <br />\n之後果D乜抗爭 依家你係總統都唔成功   之後仲有機會?   話唔定轉頭比人滅埋口<br />\n2024更加唔洗再講   下次只會赤化得更勁  作弊得更完美   到時時間又係一樣   依家都處理唔到<br />\n憑乜野覺得未來就處理到?  <br />\n所以侵侵一係就出軍隊   軍事法庭拉人封艇   如果唔敢  心軟  婦人之仁 就唔該快D認輸  <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日日出黎9叫有乜用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"538bfdc517bdd4e368608628d7149ad293f52afd","tid":2328840,"uid":130385,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T21:30:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9111d2b17bfe5d7ddf4b431ae8c76678d49bcfe8","tid":2328840,"uid":130385,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T21:35:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />比人滅口既理由都幫CNN 諗埋<br />\n因為市民太憎佢  所以就暗殺佢  <br />\n完<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da9bfa86d5df6e53a6af72ef73818959dcace5b1","tid":2328840,"uid":383914,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T21:35:44.000Z","msg":"可能侵等埋18號份報告出左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有證有據先郁手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我信侵侵一定會做野架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7560fa1e2cafcc7f2502bb4964e92b3e55bd316f","tid":2328840,"uid":33878,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"c